WEBVTT

00:00:00.240 --> 00:00:07.240
Looking for a fun data science project? Tidy Tuesday releases new datasets every week.

00:00:07.240 --> 00:00:12.480
The topics are anything from most haunted places in the USA to information on all of

00:00:12.480 --> 00:00:17.600
Taylor Swift's albums. Each dataset comes with an explanation of the data and where

00:00:17.600 --> 00:00:24.200
it comes from, a data dictionary of all the columns, and a script to clean and import

00:00:24.200 --> 00:00:31.200
the data in the R language. People share their exploration online with hashtag TidyTuesday.

00:00:32.320 --> 00:00:38.320
All data is open source and free to use and share. I'm enchanted with this project.

